  ============================================================================
  Gift Guide — Product JSON  (helper, rendered once per grid cell)
  ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
  Serialises a single product into a <script type="application/json"> blob the
  popup reads on open. Emitting a curated payload (rather than the full product
  object) keeps the DOM lean and the JS simple.

  Usage (Phase 5):
    {% render 'gift-guide-product-json', product: block.settings.product %}

  Planned payload: id, title, url, description, featured_image, options,
  and variants[{ id, title, options, available, price }].

